3月13日，OpenAI投资的人形机器人——Figure 01迎来重磅更新，接入最新版GPT后，它可以与人类全面对话，还能听、看，做家务，自主决策。

On March 13th, OpenAI's invested humanoid robot, Figure 01, received a major update.
With the integration of the latest version of GPT,
it can now fully converse with humans, as well as listen, see, perform household chores,
and make autonomous decisions.

这可能是目前最接近人类的机器人了，能自己思考、学习、与人互动。还能听、看，做家务，自主决策。在这段展示视频中，它已经初步具备当服务员的能力了。

This may be the robot that is currently closest to humans,
capable of thinking, learning, and interacting with people on its own.
It can also listen, see, perform household chores, and make autonomous decisions.

In this demo video, it has already demonstrated initial capabilities to act as a waiter.

===
在人形机器人初创公司Figure AI发布了一段视频演示。
视频中，公司研发的Figure 01机器人接入了OpenAI的大模型，能够与人类对话，理解并执行人类的指令和任务。
OpenAI模型提供高级视觉和语言智能，Figure神经网络提供快速、低级、灵巧的机器人动作。
人们惊呼：OpenAI正在掀翻机器人圈！简直就是能对话会干活的人形机器人
===

综合来看，Figure 01拥有的能力包括：
Looking at the whole picture, Figure 01's capabilities include:

一、视觉识别和理解。Visual recognition and understanding.
二、语言识别和理解。Language recognition and understanding.
三、流畅的任务执行。Smooth task execution.

